<https://example.org/article/energyUnionArticle>
    a pol:LegislativeAct ;
    pol:title "Energy Union Article" ;
    pol:text """
The article requires member states to set out national objectives, targets and contributions in five dimensions of the Energy Union: security of supply, internal energy market, research innovation and competitiveness, energy efficiency and energy climate change. These are to be expressed in terms of absolute levels with an indicative trajectory from 2021 onwards.
""" ;
    pol:hasProvision <https://example.org/article/energyUnionArticle/security> ,
                     <https://example.org/article/energyUnionArticle/market> ,
