                     <https://example.org/article/energyUnionArticle/finalEnergyConsumption>.

<https://example.org/article/energyUnionArticle/security>
    a pol:Provision ;
    pol:title "Security of Supply" ;
    pol:text """
The provision requires national objectives with regard to increasing the diversification of energy sources and supply from third countries, flexibility of the national energy system, and addressing constrained or interrupted supply.
""" .

<https://example.org/article/energyUnionArticle/market>
    a pol:Provision ;
    pol:title "Internal Energy Market" ;
    pol:text """
The provision includes electricity interconnectivity level in 2030, key infrastructure projects, and objectives related to system flexibility, market integration, smart grids, demand response, storage, distributed generation, dispatching mechanisms.
""" .

<https://example.org/article/energyUnionArticle/researchInnovation>
    a pol:Provision ;
    pol:title "Research Innovation and Competitiveness" ;
    pol:text """
