""" .

<https://example.org/article/energyUnionArticle/electrictyInterconnectivity>
    a pol:Provision ;
    pol:title "Electricity Interconnectivity" ;
    pol:text """
The provision specifies that member states aim for an electricity interconnectivity level in 2030, with a strategy from 2021 onwards defined cooperatively.
""" .

<https://example.org/article/energyUnionArticle/finalEnergyConsumption>
    a pol:Provision ;
    pol:title "Final Energy Consumption" ;
    pol:text """
The provision requires member states to express their contribution in terms of absolute level of primary and final energy consumption, with an indicative trajectory from 2021 onwards.
""" .

