    pol:isPartOf pol:Article_7 ;
    pol:text """by 31 October 2021 and every year thereafter, the commission shall assess, in particular on the basis of the information reported pursuant to this regulation, whether the union and its member states have made sufficient progress towards meeting the following requirements:
